% ====================================================================
% test_bestagon_proto_hex_math.trx -- run examples/bestagon-proto/
% proto-hex-math.trx self-test via the standard tests/ harness.
% ====================================================================
%
% Thin wrapper: loads proto-hex-math.trx (Phase 0.6A: hex coord math
% per GDD section 3), which auto-runs its self-test on load.  We just
% need to confirm the test reached its end without throwing.
%
% Asserts:
%   - pos<->cube round-trip identity on all 3 map sizes
%     (Tutorial 450 / Standard 1800 / Epic 4050 cells)
%   - pos-neighbors interior cells return exactly 6 neighbors
%     (368 + 1632 + 3796 = 5796 cells)
%   - pos-neighbors corner + edge counts on 25x18 (8 spot checks)
%   - hex-distance spec spot checks (10 cells)
%   - hex-distance symmetry on 50 random pairs
%   - hex-distance triangle inequality on 30 random triples
%
% Runs on default 1 MB VM -- test loops wrap each iteration in
% save/restore to reclaim per-cell allocation.
% ====================================================================

(examples/bestagon-proto/proto-hex-math.trx) run
(__test_ok__) =
